---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="relative z-10 w-full h-auto min-h-[4rem] py-4 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between px-6 md:px-10 backdrop-blur-md bg-white/30 border-t border-white/40 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mt-auto">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-2 md:gap-10 text-[#4a4a4a] mb-2 md:mb-0">
        <span>&copy; {currentYear} Floral Artist</span>
        <span>用植物的語言，說生活的故事</span>
    </div>
    <div class="text-[#7d8c72]">Powered by Astro + Decap CMS</div>
</footer>
